data.text: @BootlegGirl Captain George Stacy: It's a fine day to drive back and forth over the George Washington Bridge for no apparent reason.

@BootlegGirl *JONAH'S OFFICE*: young cartoonist intern walks up to his boss
JONAH: STAN! Do you have this week's strip done yet?
STAN: yes, but I also wanted to show you my new idea, a comic about a city where animal-themed marauders battle in the streets
JONAH: That's ridiculous!
@BootlegGirl Keep this up and you'll be hired as a Gotham writer.
@BootlegGirl PETER: "Um. Why is there an orange rock golem in our apartment?"
